<ns-panel decoration="">
<div class="splash">
  <h5>Enter your details</h5>
    <h1>Thank you, we’ve got nearly everything we need to start switching your energy</h1>
    <p>Just a couple more things. Please check your details below and then confirm you've read the important information before you place your order.</p> 
  </div>
<ns-form class="splash" >






